          <title>
            <string language="en">Legacies: Julia Parker</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Legacy: Julia Parker</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Legs : Julia Parker</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Legacies: Julia Parker</string>

          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">Julia Parker is one of the few remaining traditional Native American basket weavers in California. This Educator Guide traces the history of basket weaving in the West Coast Indian populations.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>

          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Julia Parker ist einer der wenigen restlichen 
traditionellen gebürtigen amerikanischen Korbweber in Kalifornien. 
Diese Erzieher-Anleitung vollzieht die Geschichte des 
Korbflechtens in den Westküste-Inderbevölkerungen nach.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Julia Parker est l'un des quelques tisserands 
américains indigènes traditionnels restants de panier en Californie.
Ce guide d'éducateur trace l'histoire de la vannerie dans les 
populations occidentales d'Indien de côte.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Julia Parker é um de poucos weavers americanos 
nativos tradicionais restantes da cesta em Califórnia. Esta 
guia do educador segue o history de tecer de cesta nas populações 
ocidentais do indian da costa.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Julia Parker è uno dei pochi tessitori americani 
natali tradizionali restanti del cestino nella California. 
Questa guida dell'educatore segue la storia di tessitura di 
cestino nelle popolazioni ad ovest dell'indiano del litorale.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Η Julia Parker είναι ένας από τους λίγους 
υπόλοιπους παραδοσιακούς εγγενείς αμερικανικούς υφαντές καλαθιών
σε Καλιφόρνια. Αυτός ο οδηγός εκπαιδευτικών επισημαίνει την
ιστορία της ύφανσης καλαθιών στους ινδικούς πληθυσμούς δυτικών 
ακτών.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Julia Parker es uno de los pocos tejedores 
americanos nativos tradicionales restantes de la cesta en California. 
Esta guía del educador rastrea la historia de la cestería en 
las poblaciones del oeste del indio de la costa.</string>
          </description>
